{"tid":2014640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"梨木樹中招66歲病人, 出街有帶眼罩口罩, CT值21","createTime":"2020-05-13T07:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T02:25:43.000Z","uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d06d5852d7a1150301d11b53ce405261de6ee9c","tid":2014640,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"即係社區有隱形帶菌者<br />\nCT value 21好毒woh<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位，關於昨天出現，令香港破功的住梨木樹66歲女病人，據內部資料顯示&hellip;&hellip;👇🏼<br />\n婆婆只到梨木树街市或到荃灣新抱家湊孫<br />\n全程眼鏡口罩<br />\n每天去荃湾楊屋道街市買餸，然後去街市街住所煮餸比新袍或仔吃<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>從不出街吃飯，出街必會帶口罩，眼罩及帽<br />\n全家無外遊紀錄</strong></span><br />\n上星期五她先發病<br />\n目前為止，找不到傳播鏈<br />\n報告顯示&hellip;&hellip;好毒<br />\nCT value:21<br />\n從未見過<br />\n*👆🏼疫情未過！！社區內有隱形帶菌者，而且可能好毒，大家出街勿掉以輕心（特別荃灣葵涌區），仍要戴口罩及勤洗手。*"},{"pid":"153c07b46c66d3a77be784fd08b11fd9c34ec4e3","tid":2014640,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"篇嘢來源係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85090f687adce42faeb8c7fede39573ed734298d","tid":2014640,"uid":114792,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"153c07b46c66d3a77be784fd08b11fd9c34ec4e3","tid":2014640,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"篇嘢來源係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"一定係藍絲group <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲字眼"},{"pid":"734417f86999d104252bab20b3759afa34cc5bba","tid":2014640,"uid":24036,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"見到d emoji 都幾乎9傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b76f5b1da359c4898b2cb02ed806e6fa0cae88d","t